  "title": "fix(autocomplete): enhance focus and keyboard behavior",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR adjusts the behavior of the autocomplete widget when interacted with:\r\n\r\n- refines with the input value if there is no active selection\r\n- first <kbd>Escape</kbd> closes the panel, the second clears the selection\r\n- first <kbd>Enter</kbd> closes the panel, the second blurs the input\r\n- keeps focus on clear\r\n\r\nFX-3579",
